<C>__{kurtz}
<P>__{(continuing; looking up in pain)}
<D>__{you see how stupid it would have been to blow out my brains? i'm dying from the gut anyway.}
<A>__{willard quickly prepares another shot. kurtz, truly frightened, holds up his hand.}
<C>__{kurtz}
