<P>__{(looks at him)}
<D>__{yes, you know why.}
<P>__{(he looks)}
<D>__{your mission makes about as much sense as those idiots who sent you on it. asshole ! schmuck ! how long does it take you to figure out that nobody knows what they're doing here.}
